stats_texts.title: Global Benchmark Statistics
stats_texts.explain_stats_list_1:
Basis: {{count}} data points | As of: {{lastUpdate}}

* **Mean ({{mean}}):** The arithmetic average of all results.
* **p90 ({{p90}}):** Excellence threshold. Only 10% of all websites reach a score of {{p90}} or higher.
* **p75 ({{p75}}):** Above average. 25% of websites reach a score of {{p75}} or higher.
* **p50 ({{p50}}):** Median (Center). 50% of websites reach a score of {{p50}} or higher.
* **p25 ({{p25}}):** Below average. 75% of websites reach a score of {{p25}} or higher.
* **p10 ({{p10}}):** Low level. 90% of websites reach a score of {{p10}} or higher.
